{"tid":19583,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇有留意心學","createTime":"2016-12-03T01:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T00:42:53.000Z","uid":46983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"208db7b320787e09efc1c5fd355ed5ec08a6a4c7","tid":19583,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"「陸王心學」是由儒家學者陸九淵、王陽明（王守仁）發展出來的心學的簡稱，或直接稱「心學」；或有專門稱為某哲學家的心學，如王陽明的「陽明心學」。<br />\n<br />\n陸王心學與程朱理學雖有時同屬宋明理學之下，但多有分歧，陸解說宇宙二字為：「宇宙內事乃己分內事；己分內事乃宇宙內事。」陸主張「吾心即是宇宙」，又倡「心即理」說。斷言「天理、人理、物理只在吾心之中。人同此心，心同此理。往古來今，概莫能外。」認為治學的方法，主要是發明本心，不必多讀書外求，「學苟知本，六經皆我註腳。」皆與朱熹主張大相逕庭。<br />\n<br />\n陸王心學往往被認為是儒學中的「格心派」（中共馬列主義思想政治教材將其歸類為「主觀唯心主義」），而程朱理學為「格物派」（中共教材將其歸類為「客觀唯心主義」）。<br />\n<br />\n陽明學\t編輯<br />\n王陽明早年長期鑽研朱子學而無所成，而後因為參悟了陸九淵的學說，因而廣大發揚，是為陽明學。主要主張由王陽明於史上著名的「龍場悟道」而得，其門人各放異彩，可分作左右二派。<br />\n<br />\n王守仁嗰句知行合一真係好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dd3121c2073b777973eb43cb1e6eed4d65bfed","tid":19583,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人 標題打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"10505935d64a99804092f18ec75061bb5b65e663","tid":19583,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80e02537a639d524a1b7a032e34c1549b709c27","tid":19583,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21e02feddb37608d22c14129cb3fae5cc022a71","tid":19583,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"何謂知行合一?<br />\n行指實踐?"},{"pid":"4a9701225333d8935258e935fbbda7b176067b82","tid":19583,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何謂知行合一?<br />\n行指實踐?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道理解左之後就要做 知道但係唔做係假知"},{"pid":"dd08f4577efdc3320d2f9d1d6e9a3dfc50c33bc3","tid":19583,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>何謂知行合一?<br />\n行指實踐?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道理解左之後就要做 知道但係唔做係假知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsor唔係好明有咩咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8accdb50367ca95f6dd920af7ca0fcffd70e560","tid":19583,"uid":44503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"碌鳩淵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dfb3e36e068b374b606bdc89727e613f54d451","tid":19583,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b6c27839d0cc0f705aee3e8e01c6ba081ff1bc2f","tid":19583,"uid":46983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>何謂知行合一?<br />\n行指實踐?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道理解左之後就要做 知道但係唔做係假知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsor唔係好明有咩咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔係好好明所以po上黎睇下有冇人有研究"},{"pid":"0e004bebe29248dd2cb9025a4f0fc2a22048c96a","tid":19583,"uid":38324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>何謂知行合一?<br />\n行指實踐?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道理解左之後就要做 知道但係唔做係假知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsor唔係好明有咩咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢個概念<br />\n應該係純粹要反抗朱熹條撚屌叫人咩撚都格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n王守仁：「你班腐儒 你地日格夜格都冇用㗎啦 坐言起行啦屌」<br />\n<br />\n睇武道狂之詩接觸心學 <br />\n留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99685ef91e16ec7a4eaf95fe79f0e83242db98c","tid":19583,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>何謂知行合一?<br />\n行指實踐?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道理解左之後就要做 知道但係唔做係假知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsor唔係好明有咩咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢個概念<br />\n應該係純粹要反抗朱熹條撚屌叫人咩撚都格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n王守仁：「你班腐儒 你地日格夜格都冇用㗎啦 坐言起行啦屌」<br />\n<br />\n睇武道狂之詩接觸心學 <br />\n留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係反朱熹本人，係反後面班偽君子。<br />\n朱熹講「先知後行」都係需要實踐，<br />\n但後面班人不斷搵藉口拖延唔做，<br />\n所以王守仁先講兩者係唔可以分開。<br />\n<br />\n以前上堂讀過，大概係咁。"},{"pid":"2bfee138611ce9cb82024baec84b8b5ace113948","tid":19583,"uid":38324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>何謂知行合一?<br />\n行指實踐?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道理解左之後就要做 知道但係唔做係假知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsor唔係好明有咩咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢個概念<br />\n應該係純粹要反抗朱熹條撚屌叫人咩撚都格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n王守仁：「你班腐儒 你地日格夜格都冇用㗎啦 坐言起行啦屌」<br />\n<br />\n睇武道狂之詩接觸心學 <br />\n留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係反朱熹本人，係反後面班偽君子。<br />\n朱熹講「先知後行」都係需要實踐，<br />\n但後面班人不斷搵藉口拖延唔做，<br />\n所以王守仁先講兩者係唔可以分開。<br />\n<br />\n以前上堂讀過，大概係咁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陸王心學有冇啲咩書入門<br />\n對佢認識都係基於維基同明朝那些事兒本嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e010d4133775bc08d5957e7fc4c63b73b199ab3","tid":19583,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>何謂知行合一?<br />\n行指實踐?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道理解左之後就要做 知道但係唔做係假知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsor唔係好明有咩咁特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢個概念<br />\n應該係純粹要反抗朱熹條撚屌叫人咩撚都格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n王守仁：「你班腐儒 你地日格夜格都冇用㗎啦 坐言起行啦屌」<br />\n<br />\n睇武道狂之詩接觸心學 <br />\n留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係反朱熹本人，係反後面班偽君子。<br />\n朱熹講「先知後行」都係需要實踐，<br />\n但後面班人不斷搵藉口拖延唔做，<br />\n所以王守仁先講兩者係唔可以分開。<br />\n<br />\n以前上堂讀過，大概係咁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陸王心學有冇啲咩書入門<br />\n對佢認識都係基於維基同明朝那些事兒本嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無咁學術可以讀：<br />\n《王陽明靖亂錄》（古文傳記，網上有）<br />\n《王陽明新語》（當代半傳記，半小說）<br />\n下面個本雖然比較厚，但寫得好立體，<br />\n可以了解王守仁內心掙扎，同悟道的波折經歷。<br />\n<br />\n學術就可以讀：<br />\n陳來《宋明理學》<br />\n陳來《有無之境－－王陽明哲學的精神》"},{"pid":"c3a6cb323986616d125351ef62297a49016c2620","tid":19583,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"守仁格竹都係一件重要事件來<br />\n<br />\n不單止講出格物嘅難度(冇普遍性) 更加講出知而不行嘅弊病<br />\n<br />\n王學主張人有天性 唔可能亦唔應該為左思想而放棄天性"},{"pid":"7a87c57bd1bdb39b29a91bff71e7a47802978c05","tid":19583,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:47:09.000Z","msg":"心學同理學其實唔係對立<br />\n南宋有鵝湖之辯，有陸九齡、陸九淵同朱熹見面到最後無明確勝負之分<br />\n而上面巴打提到陳來本《宋明理學》講到中唐後有三件大事影響中國文化，分別係新禪宗運動、古文運動同新儒家運動(理學)<br />\n利申：識好少，想黎學野，有錯請指正"},{"pid":"f81845e9d8d68c2019ce467ecad523880f863316","tid":19583,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:11:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1321fbec59ea74bb284bbb0287a07de709e2c48","tid":19583,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心學同理學其實唔係對立<br />\n南宋有鵝湖之辯，有陸九齡、陸九淵同朱熹見面到最後無明確勝負之分<br />\n而上面巴打提到陳來本《宋明理學》講到中唐後有三件大事影響中國文化，分別係新禪宗運動、古文運動同新儒家運動(理學)<br />\n利申：識好少，想黎學野，有錯請指正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n詳細情況我唔記得，但有一次講學，<br />\n陸九淵同朱熹係有d 惺惺相識。<br />\n立場唔同，但個目標都係一致。<br />\n主要分歧係天理係外面，定係內心。<br />\n<br />\n利申：我都識好少，只係興趣讀物"},{"pid":"01c20b425d887559ffcc5a14c188df294c97eb96","tid":19583,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3848e097243e97d0fdb605d233ae2a8c01f47948","tid":19583,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"講多少少，唐代思想係重視現實政治，認為一個強大政權先會令世界有秩序。而宋代較著重個人修養，較重視個人修義，認為係靠自己的改變先會令社會改變。有錯請指正"},{"pid":"96750695ed36873f62fbe5eafac6b80bb970d1d7","tid":19583,"uid":4813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講多少少，唐代思想係重視現實政治，認為一個強大政權先會令世界有秩序。而宋代較著重個人修養，較重視個人修義，認為係靠自己的改變先會令社會改變。有錯請指正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱交左份功課寫唐宋變革，係思想史角度，唐代既人覺得文學創作包含左係以往累積既傳統入面，討論價值觀只係搵邊一種文化較為合適。而係宋代，人轉向相信心既能力，借此可以由事物既內蘊同自我中心既道德品質到搵到正確既觀念。"},{"pid":"27406bbd357772ab6129a19097e9dcc4fe189127","tid":19583,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:08:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdc0b1f70a611e55635fcdc2b32ccf4f8013a6dc","tid":19583,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:37:13.000Z","msg":"王陽明心學可以用四句教來總結：<br />\n<br />\n無善無惡心之體，有善有惡意之動，知善知惡是良知，為善去惡是格物。<br />\n<br />\n心體無善相惡相，故此是純善之心。此心即為良知，側隱之心。宋明理學喜用天道性命相貫通來講心，此心即是天道，天道就係係心上程現出來。<br />\n<br />\n朱子同王陽明最大既分別就係前者是性即理，後者係心即理。 前者需通過格物窮理，去格外界既物而見天理次所在。後者就是說明天性即在本心，良知內，並不需要向外求天理。<br />\n<br />\n想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c10f3613b764411fe8a2410df2834afa42109b","tid":19583,"uid":36283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王陽明心學可以用四句教來總結：<br />\n<br />\n無善無惡心之體，有善有惡意之動，知善知惡是良知，為善去惡是格物。<br />\n<br />\n心體無善相惡相，故此是純善之心。此心即為良知，側隱之心。宋明理學喜用天道性命相貫通來講心，此心即是天道，天道就係係心上程現出來。<br />\n<br />\n朱子同王陽明最大既分別就係前者是性即理，後者係心即理。 前者需通過格物窮理，去格外界既物而見天理次所在。後者就是說明天性即在本心，良知內，並不需要向外求天理。<br />\n<br />\n想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知"},{"pid":"6584da0ae4649dd80176347f4eee9f152f169d45","tid":19583,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>王陽明心學可以用四句教來總結：<br />\n<br />\n無善無惡心之體，有善有惡意之動，知善知惡是良知，為善去惡是格物。<br />\n<br />\n心體無善相惡相，故此是純善之心。此心即為良知，側隱之心。宋明理學喜用天道性命相貫通來講心，此心即是天道，天道就係係心上程現出來。<br />\n<br />\n朱子同王陽明最大既分別就係前者是性即理，後者係心即理。 前者需通過格物窮理，去格外界既物而見天理次所在。後者就是說明天性即在本心，良知內，並不需要向外求天理。<br />\n<br />\n想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然心是無善無惡既天道，那麽人為甚麼會有善惡?問題係係意果到。意即係心之所發， 心本是無善無惡，但係心一起念，即係意，依個意就係有善相惡相之分。 王陽明既致良知教就係係到開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲d再打"}]}